description.en:
BullionsChain are building a cryptocurrency to precious metals exchange where users can buy, sell, hedge or stake cryptocurrencies or precious metals. The BLC token built on the Ethereum blockchain idea has been designed and developed to reward token holders with BCG (BullionsChain Gold) and other physically backed digital representations of precious metals on a daily basis. 
Whilst also providing cheaper transactions  and discounted rates on the exchange with BLC.
